You've caught up.
Seems I've been toying too much with my prey.
Bah... That was unintended.
You'll have to find another path. Think of it as an added test of your resourcefulness...
Prove you are worthy to rule!
Chronicles of eld... Recount the fury of erupting peaks!
Chronicles of eld... Retell the hunger of roiling waters!
Chronicles of eld... Recall the cruelty of merciless storms!
I will take the measure of your resolve!
Implacable strength of the mountain be mine...
Spirit of my brethren, your thunder roars!
That you should endure my fury...
Feel the weight of history carved in stone!
我が守り、崩せるか……！？

Travelers on the mountain? How delightful!
Do stay and play a while!
Come to me, snowkin! Join the fun!
Wait for it... Now, freeze!
雪玉固めて、ゴロゴロドーン！
Come to me, snowkin, large and small!

I see you've arrived. Follow the path and you'll soon see the entrance. Be careful now.
Whew, the diversion did the trick. Let's push straight to the middle level!
There should be another freight elevator further in. Use it to head up.
Oh dear, this one looks like trouble...
It's nothing they can't handle. I'll activate the elevator to keep you moving.
You make it look so easy!
It'll get tougher from here, though, so stay on your toes.
A dead end? No, wait...
Warning. Please present identification. Failure to comply will result in the use of force.
According to our data, this is where souls are stripped of memories...
Indeed. The souls are the white matter, and they're being sent to Zoraal Ja.
Well done. The conveyors up ahead should take you to the upper level.
I'm afraid this is where our data ends. You're on your own now.
That they should make it past Deceiver... Soldiers, hold them off!
Researcher evacuation complete! Release all test subjects!
Intruders detected. Initializing all turrets and support units.
Engaging hostiles.
Deploying support units. Initiating cover fire.
Active camouflage operational.
Deploying turrets. Initiating suppressive fire.
Maintaining 80% coordination rate.
Increasing sub-weapon output.
Intruders still remain. Transmitting emergency code.
To be deleted
Filthy rebels! You will not reach the king!
My psychokinesis will bring you to your knees!
Forming directional gravity field!
Stubborn vermin... I will deal with you yet!
Disabling limiter. Increasing psychokinesis potency!
Unnngh... My head...feels like to split...
Why!? Why won't you die!?
Graaagggh! I must win...or else my souls...

Defeat His Royal Headness Leonogg I
Arrive at the Party Plaza
Defeat Jack-in-the-Pot
Arrive at the Restive Hall
Defeat Träumerei
Bow down to my flawless noggin─your king decrees it!
Join us, and be crowned in splendor!
I-Impossible! You would deny my regal, royal headness!?
Behold! Your noggin is made new!
Little lords! Little ladies! Let us proffer our heads in friendship!
Open your mind, and let us bestow upon you a glorious noggin...
I-Inconceivable! Why must you refuse our companionship!?
A most splendid noggin! You are worthy of my court!
Oh, little lords and ladies...your king has need of you!
All shall be blessed with nogginhood!
You dare defy my royal decree!? Have you no sense!?
Grrr... I can tolerate your unsightly pate no longer! Off with your head! Off with it, I say!
One among you has refused nogginhood...
A pristine noggin indeed... But you mustn't let its beauty go to your head! Ohoho!
I shall not rest until my every subject bears a beauteous noggin!
Cleanse the unsightly one! There is no escaping our brilliance!
Ah, yes... A glorious, noddling noodle, as befits my kingdom!
Apologies for breaking character, but...perhaps it's time you stopped resisting? There are limits to my patience.
...How many times must I tell you to stand still? Nogginhood doesn't hurt! I swear it!
\\<sob> Please, just...let me kill you! LET ME KILL YOU!
Greetings, goodly guests! Your tea awaits!
I've not had company in ages... This calls for my finest cups!
Cheers! A frightful toast to you and yours!

Round and round, the cups shall go!
Where they stop? Why, no one knows!
Drink all you like─I guarantee my brew is to die for!
Good-bye, my subjects...and good night...
'Tis our duty to seize the nogginless!
Yesterday is gone, yet tomorrow never comes... So sleep, child, and drown in nightmares everlasting.
Defy me as you wish. It will not wake you from this misery.
I see it shall take more than honeyed words to lull you to your eternal sleep...
Spirits of eternal reverie, to me!
Allow me to offer my aid! Step into the light, and become as a ghost to pass through all things corporeal!
But ware Träumerei's magicks... Should you sense danger, return to my beacons, and your mortal flesh shall be restored!
Welcome one and all to the land of waking dreams and nightmares! Please form a single-file line as you enter.
A word to our guests: Strayborough is open for all eternity! Answer your heart's every desire, and dream your days─or your life─away!
Hear ye, hear ye! His Royal Headness Leonogg I graces us with his presence!
Lost souls of every age, the Frolicking Grounds is your whimsical stage! Do be careful not to lose yourself in our phantasmal attractions!
Attention, all dreamers─you are cordially invited to Jack-in-the-Pot's enchanted tea party!
You have entered the Endless House... Fear not, for I shall guide you through its haunted halls.
You are a formidable slayer of ghosts...but have you the strength to best their master?
Beyond this hall lies Träumerei, Lord of Nightmares.
Heed my words, and together, we shall end his reign of terror!

There was a boat like ours up ahead.
Could be Zoraal Ja, or... Oh gods, is it Bakool Ja Ja?
Forget who else is on the river right now─we have company!
We're in for some rain, it seems...
Yes, come closer! We have something for you...

Gah, this is not going to plan!
We'll just have to improvise...
See you upriver...if you make it that far!

The harness is broken.
I'm sorry, but we have to pull over to the bank.
See if there's a route overland. We'll try to catch up to you later!
What strange happenstance. Hath some misfortune befallen thy vessel?
Apologies, friends─it seems you'll be taking the long way around!
That is Bakool Ja Ja ahead of us! Be ready for anything!
Crippling our boat was a cowardly move...
Erenville! We're losing speed!
We won't be going anywhere until we can make repairs.
A gift! Courtesy of the blessed siblings!
Defeat the Dawnservant!
Give it your all─I want a fight to remember!
Let's test the waters!
They didn't even blink.
You can do better than that!
Have you ever fought a viper?
I see you know the viper style...
Hah! Let's see how you handle this!
The spearman did not lie. Very well, then!
Resolve and Reason kindle...
Oh, right.
No more holding back!
We're far from finished!
Hah! Did you think you had my measure?
You fight well indeed!
You really are formidable!
Now we'll see what you're truly made of...
That will do! You've shown me more than enough!
Hraaaaaargh!

Rats... There are rats!
Workers, arise! Eliminate the rats!
Smash them! Smear them into pulp!
Silence... Our workers have fallen... Activate Firearms!
Core engaged... Firearms is risen!
Hahaha, such power! Destroy, destroy, destroy!
By enchanted sledge, intruders begone! Begone, begone, begone!
Burn upon the mettlegrounds! Burn, burn, burn!
Crumble beneath my full might! Die, die, die!

Defeat Apyaahi
We have to take care of these beasts before going after Apyaahi!
Over here, <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>!
I need help over here!
As I feared... My creatures cannot live up to the real thing.
How about this?
A tenacious lot, aren't you? Well, I suppose I wouldn't want you to fall too quickly.
There are so many...but we will persevere!
I can smother them in flames. Lend me your protection!
Scheming, are we? Don't think I'll allow you to do as you please.
No! My poor, pitiful pets!
So I cannot rely on numbers alone... Keep them distracted, my darlings!
We'll be fine. Go after Apyaahi!
I might be in trouble...
Something a little different this time. Behold the fruits of my travels across Tural.
Thanks for the help! Now to catch Apyaahi!
Don't think you've won yet.
You're strong, to be sure. But so is this!
Send your worst─I won't lose!
Don't hold back! My medicines will keep you upright!
Limits are just more rules to be broken!
That doesn't look good...
Worry not. Get behind me, and you'll be safe!
You...you survived that!?
Bah, even bugs squirm before they die. This time I'll finish things!
You're as stubborn as the mud stuck to my sandals... Yet that alone is not enough to─ What?
Something's gotten into them...
I admit... I may have underestimated you lot.
And while defeating you would be quite the feather in my cap, the gates of Tuliyollal are a much easier target...
Curses, she's making a run for it! Follow her, <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>!
Anything that would obstruct the free world I aim to create will be destroyed!
Go forth, my prickly punisher, and crush those who would bind us!
...My, but what is this sudden, dreadful feeling...? Perhaps I haven't been sleeping well as of late.
Impressive. I expected no less of you. But this farce ends here!
Now, smash <If(PlayerParameter(4))>her<Else/>him</If> to a pulp!
I don't think so!
So you find comfort in fellowship. At least this will save me the trouble of killing you one by one.
This is your moment, my pointy pugilist!
Ungh... It's getting even stronger!
<split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, we are at your back! Together we'll repel this foul creature!
Keep going, everyone!
How...how can you stand before the treasure's might!? What are you!?
Such power...power that would be welcome within the Passage of the Unbound!
Victory is mine! Now do you know the beauty of true freedom!?
Do not falter, my spiky soldier!
Gather around <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, everyone!
Can you withstand this!?
Spread out, or we'll be swept away!
You scurry about like rats! Pulverize them with this, my barbed barbarian!
Is this...poison? Stay away from it!
No... Even my spiny savior has fallen...
Grrr! I'm not finished yet! I can replenish my ranks!
Crush them underfoot!
I'll end this in a single blow!
Attacking from above!? Devious...
Leave the skies to me. The rest of you, focus on the big one!
No, I think not.

To the memories of better days, I bid farewell...
Have you heard? Princess Sphene is here!

Your smile means all is right with the world.
If I smile, it is because you all smile for me.

Initiating security protocol.
You are my people, and I will protect you.
The painful memories of war, I lay to rest...
Quickly, take shelter in the castle!
Foreign entities detected. Proceeding with removal.
Is anyone still out here?
There are people over there! Bring us closer!
It's too dangerous! You must flee!
Don't worry about me! Just save yourself!
May we meet again, Your Highness!
Security breach confirmed. Initiating level five security protocol.
Fear not. You will all live on.
And at the last, my final...\\<bzzzt>...an Endless...
Foreign enti...detected. Initiating...rity protocol.
They've done it! They've preserved the queen's...
We can't give up! Not until...keep...complete...

Alert. Alert. Intruders detected. Engaging defense turrets.
Vanguard is under attack! Vanguard is under attack! All units prepare for battle!
Enemy sighted. R7 sentries, prepare to engage.
Dammit all... Power the Crossbridge and release the beasts! We can stop them there!
Send in reinforcements! The commander will not tolerate failure!
Warning: intruders detected. Initializing extermination protocol.
Wingblade engaged. Preparing high-speed maneuvers.
Redeploying wingblade. Thrusters engaged.
Combat proficiency exceeds expected parameters. Requesting reinforcements.
Authorization to disengage limiters granted. All units─commence firing.
All units─prepare for aerial bombardment.
Initiating secondary directive: electrope weapon testing.
You truly believe yourself a match for us? The audacity!
On your knees!
You still stand. Impressive...
H-How...? How could you... Ugh...
All right. No more games!
You'll pay for the souls you've made me waste this day.
Give up now and I'll make this quick!
None can survive the serpent's art!
